Results are summarized as a percentage change and the p value for variables relating to: strength outcomes, RE, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
